{"tid":1842303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 醫護罷工要幾多人先成事？","createTime":"2020-01-25T15:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T02:54:13.000Z","uid":197157,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9031f18f6f1b7f9025d57a27f0937afb5498e88c","tid":1842303,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:19:14.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工要脅封關呢件事已經講咗幾日<br />\n但其實要有幾多人肯罷工先會成功？<br />\n<br />\n以下個人愚見：<br />\n其實淨係最先抽中生死籤嘅人罷工，已經會成功<br />\n我嘅推論是咁的&darr;<br />\n1. 抽中生死籤嘅人罷工（或者辭職）<br />\n2. 好自然要另一班人頂上<br />\n3. 呢班人本身一定係抽唔中嗰班，但係突然要頂上<br />\n4. 心入面一定會有不滿，覺得點解係自己／點解本身抽中生死籤嘅人罷工就可以冇事<br />\n5. 返返去第一步<br />\n<br />\n個結果會變成愈來愈多人罷工<br />\n當然一定會有願意留低既人，但只要頭一、兩轉夠多人罷<br />\n由於人手少咗，後面嘅人唔罷嘅成本就會愈嚟愈高，變相愈容易選擇罷工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n大家有冇其他諗法？"},{"pid":"fbb736287f48b8a4205fcb482f1521afcb0f06e3","tid":1842303,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"推，認真Post嚟"},{"pid":"1071f26eadc1b00ff01889252fe69de0bb28b89f","tid":1842303,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"推（1/10）"},{"pid":"b7b5b194b68f97bced5aa72e77fd647d58477a62","tid":1842303,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"推（2/10）"},{"pid":"c4cf761e9094aca069b3d84706239c5dda04159f","tid":1842303,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:23:41.000Z","msg":"推（3/10）"},{"pid":"8f5423020e5df17291728f1782f57a7267d12f63","tid":1842303,"uid":162380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:24:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"90b99b6c4df7ca8a152f97ddbef24aed64f1f0c6","tid":1842303,"uid":162380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:24:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3d4417e040bac5d42eb0fa9ee7db7843df98cdb6","tid":1842303,"uid":162380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"<